  "texts": [
    "• An agent, which learns from the interaction with its environment over a discrete sequence of time steps T = {0, 1, 2,...} and that pursues a certain objective.",
    "• An environment, defined as any element external to the agent.",
    "It is a dynamic process that produces relevant data for the agent.",
    "A state s t ∈ S represents the current situation of the environment at time step t. • A set of actions A, which determine the dynamics of the environment.",
    "Every action a t ∈ A allows the agent to transit between different states."
  ],
